[https://github.com/rags/toggle-test/blob/master/toggle-test.el test-toggle.el] allows you to quickly switch between test and test subject. This is a very useful tool to have when you are TDDing. Test Toggle is similar to test toggle functionality provided by !IntelliJ and other !JetBrains IDEs.

You can find complete documentation and the source [https://github.com/rags/toggle-test on github]
